title: DVDFab Passkey for DVD/Blu-Ray 8.2.5.1 + Serial
description:
DVDFab Passkey for DVD/Blu-Ray 8.2.5.1 (Latest)

Passkey for DVD

DVDFab Passkey for Blu-Ray is a Windowsd-based driver that works on-the-fly to unprotect encrypted DVD/Blu-Ray disks. It can remove all known DVD/Blu-Ray copy protections and region codes just in seconds to help you watch any DVD movie with no limitation.

Passkey for DVD can help also rip DVD to hard disk, and allows you to use any software, including DVDFab DVD Copy and DVD Ripper, to access unencrypted DVD contents to copy, burn, clone item, and so on.


Features:

- Remove all known DVD protections
- Allow you to freely view any DVD and rip DVD to hard disk
- Work with other software like DVDFab DVD Copy and DVD Ripper, to access unencrypted DVD content


Passkey for Blu-Ray

Passkey for Blu-Ray, as a Windows-bassed driver, decrypts any Blu-Ray disk in just seconds to allow you to use other compatible software to deal with now unprotected content. It works well with DVDFab Blu-Ray Copy, Blu-Ray Ripper, and many other apps.

What's more, Passkey for Blu-Ray can rip Blu-Ray disks to your hard disk all by itself. And you can view your favorite Blu-Ray movies on you region specific player which can be set "Multi-Region" with the help of Passkey for Blu-Ray.


Features:

- Remove all known Blu-Ray protections
- Help you watch any Blu-Ray with no region limit and rip Blu-Ray to hard disk
- Work with other software like Blu-Ray Copy, Blu-Ray Ripper to access unencrypted Blu-Ray content


Changelog: Release date v8.2.5.1 (2015-10-20)


- NEW: Added support for new Java protections



OS: Windows XP/Vista/7/8/8.1/10


Language: Multilingual
